Methylene Blue IV
Everything you need to know about your methylene blue infusion —
mitochondrial support at the cellular level.
Price: $450
Duration: 30–60 minutes

THE BASICS

What Is Methylene Blue?
Methylene Blue is one of the oldest pharmaceutical compounds, now being
used for its powerful effects on mitochondrial function.
It acts as an alternative electron carrier in the mitochondrial electron transport chain —
essentially giving your cells a backup power source. When mitochondria aren''t
working efficiently, you feel it as brain fog, fatigue, and slow recovery. Methylene blue
helps your cells produce energy even when normal pathways are impaired.

HOW IT WORKS

What Methylene Blue Does
Targets your cells'' energy production at the most fundamental level.


⚡ Electron Transport
Donates and accepts electrons in the mitochondrial electron transport chain —
supporting ATP (cellular energy) production even when normal pathways are
impaired.

🧠 Crosses Blood-Brain Barrier
One of the few compounds that crosses the blood-brain barrier, directly
supporting brain cell energy and cognitive function.

🛡️ Antioxidant Properties
Acts as an antioxidant and anti-inflammatory, protecting cells from oxidative
damage while supporting repair.

🔋 Cellular Energy
Supports ATP production — the energy currency every cell in your body needs to
function. More efficient mitochondria = more energy.

PRICING

Methylene Blue IV
METHYLENE BLUE IV


$450
30–60 minute infusion. Direct mitochondrial support for
energy, clarity, and cellular function.

INSTRUCTIONS

What to Know Before Your Session
1

Medication Check
Inform your provider of ALL medications — especially SSRIs, SNRIs, and MAOIs.
This is critical for your safety.

2

Hydrate
Drink plenty of water before and after your session. Hydration supports absorption
and recovery.

3

Expect the Blue
Your urine and potentially skin may have a blue-green tint for 24–48 hours after
infusion. This is completely normal and expected.

4

Relax
Session takes 30–60 minutes. Bring something to read or watch. You''ll be
comfortable the entire time.

TIMELINE


What to Expect
Mitochondrial benefits build with regular sessions.

During/After Infusion
Some notice improved clarity and alertness during or shortly after the session.

24–72 Hours
Enhanced energy, reduced brain fog. Your mitochondria are producing energy more
efficiently.

Regular Sessions
Cumulative mitochondrial benefits. Sustained improvements in energy, clarity, and
cognitive function.

SAFETY

Important Safety Information
Do Not Use If You:
✕ Take SSRIs, SNRIs, or MAOIs (risk of serotonin syndrome)
✕ Take other serotonergic medications
✕ Have G6PD deficiency
✕ Are pregnant or breastfeeding


Possible Side Effects:
• Blue-green urine and stool (normal, expected)
• Temporary blue-green skin tint
• Mild nausea
• Temporary headache
The blue discoloration is completely harmless and resolves within 24–48 hours. Inform your
provider of ALL medications before treatment.

Important: Individual results vary. These treatments are not FDA-approved to diagnose, treat,
cure, or prevent any disease.

Questions? We''re Here.
