cycle, whether you''re approaching perimenopause, and what''s actually driving your
symptoms. We add advanced cardiac markers like ApoB and Lp(a) that most primary
care doctors never order. Combined with a full thyroid panel, fasting insulin,
inflammation markers, and a complete vitamin and mineral panel, this gives us the
most thorough baseline possible to build a real plan.

